â€¢ Previously averaging regular visits

**To keep you motivated:**
â€¢ NEW: Try our just-launched HIIT classes (perfect for busy schedules!)
â€¢ Book a complimentary fitness assessment to update your goals
â€¢ 20% off personal training packages this month

